WEBVTT

00:02.420 --> 00:04.160
MOHINDER:
Previously on Heroes.

00:04.255 --> 00:05.916
PETER: Our lives
as we knew them are over.

00:06.090 --> 00:08.456
Now, to survive this thing,
we gotta go totally
off the grid.

00:08.551 --> 00:09.586
Where did you get these?

00:09.677 --> 00:10.666
MOHINDER: Matt.

00:10.761 --> 00:13.218
He drew them
right after the crash.
He has Isaac's gift.

00:13.306 --> 00:15.467
HIRO: Is this India?
MATT: You're right.

00:15.600 --> 00:17.090
It is my destiny
to go there.

00:17.185 --> 00:19.016
You're going back
to Costa Verde,
young lady.

00:19.103 --> 00:22.812
So I get a pass,
and everyone I know
just disappears.

00:23.149 --> 00:24.184
TRACY: Nathan, it's me.

00:24.275 --> 00:25.435
I want my old life back.

00:25.526 --> 00:28.484
I give you Peter, my part
in this gets written off
as "never happened."

00:29.322 --> 00:30.732
You can trust me, Tracy.

00:30.823 --> 00:33.360
You said you were alone.
I know.

00:33.451 --> 00:35.692
How many times
are we gonna do this?

00:35.786 --> 00:36.946
(WHOOSHING)

00:38.372 --> 00:39.623
What did we ever
do to you?

00:39.749 --> 00:40.989
Nothing.

00:41.083 --> 00:42.619
Wrong place, wrong time.

00:43.002 --> 00:44.117
(GRUNTING)

00:44.378 --> 00:45.754
(SCREAMING)

00:45.838 --> 00:48.705
SYLAR: You just killed
the one shot I had
at finding my old man.

00:48.883 --> 00:49.998
I know where he is.

00:50.092 --> 00:52.299
Your mom
have a car?

00:52.386 --> 00:53.421
Not anymore.

00:53.846 --> 00:55.711
(CELL PHONE RINGING)

01:08.653 --> 01:12.521
It is so nice
to have everyone under
the same roof again.

01:13.115 --> 01:16.152
Noah, I hope this
new job will keep you
home for a while.

01:16.369 --> 01:17.779
Absolutely.

01:18.955 --> 01:22.288
What does
a consultant do,
exacﬂy?

01:28.089 --> 01:32.082
