and government people.

01:32.301 --> 01:38.467
They explain their
overall strategies and
objectives and l consult.

01:41.435 --> 01:45.019
Honey, do you have
to do that at the table?
Sorry.

01:47.733 --> 01:51.601
So, I have yet
to hear word one
about your trip.

01:52.321 --> 01:53.561
Claire?

01:56.450 --> 01:57.781
Nothing much to tell.

01:57.868 --> 02:02.737
You visited five of the best
colleges on the East Coast
and you have nothing to tell?

02:07.545 --> 02:09.536
Which ones did you like, Noah?

02:11.549 --> 02:12.755
Brown.

02:16.345 --> 02:17.881
I liked Brown.

02:20.641 --> 02:23.724
Claire.
Come back here.

02:27.606 --> 02:32.396
I think all this
Ivy League talk might be
a little intimidating.

02:32.486 --> 02:35.944
Maybe community
college would be
a better fit for now.

02:36.032 --> 02:37.442
I'll go talk to her.

